{"tid":1695033,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"內地限未成年玩家網遊充值額度　每晚10時後不准打機","createTime":"2019-11-05T11:50:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T19:59:27.000Z","uid":141060,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fa13cec4f611ef996882c7381965eadfd0d77243","tid":1695033,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T11:50:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20191105/bkn-20191105163959082-1105_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20191105%2Fbkn-20191105163959082-1105_00952_001.html&d=YDk3w6YkG5F4GHIJWz3fGKGvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=44e4934c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20191105/bkn-20191105163959082-1105_00952_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20191105/photo/bkn-20191105163959082-1105_00952_001_01p.jpg?20191105175946\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20191105%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20191105163959082-1105_00952_001_01p.jpg%3F20191105175946&h=e32fca22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n內地近年不時發生兒童偷走家長血汗錢，偷偷為網絡遊戲充值的事件，屢屢引起爭議。國家新聞出版署近日印發《關於防止未成年人沉迷網絡遊戲的通知》（下稱《通知》），限制網絡遊戲平台向未成年人提供服務的時段、時長及增值付費；更要求所有網絡遊戲玩家均須實名註冊遊戲帳號。<br />\n《通知》指出，網遊企業不得為未滿8歲玩家提供付費服務；至於8歲至15歲的玩家，每次充值不得超過50元（人民幣．下同，約56港元），每月累計充值金額不得超過200元（約230港元）；16歲或以上的未成年玩家，單次充值金額不得超過100元（約113港元），每月累計充值金額不得超過400元（約455港元）。<br />\n在遊戲時段及時長方面，禁止遊戲平台每晚10時至次日上午8時，為未成年玩家提供遊戲服務；法定節假日每日不得超過3小時，其餘每日不得超過1.5小時。《通知》指出，該標準是從合理分配未成年人日常作息時間角度提出，除去正常睡眠、學習、用餐及文體活動時間外，區分節假日和其他時間，對遊戲時段時長予以限定。<br />\n《通知》同時要求所有網絡遊戲玩家均須實名註冊遊戲帳號，須以有效身份訊息方可註冊及進入遊戲；並要求學校、家長履行未成年人監護責任，幫助他們樹立正確的網絡遊戲消費觀念和行為習慣。"},{"pid":"cdf139c33d2ee6253e14b497402d4ec7a7f8c1a4","tid":1695033,"uid":263261,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T11:53:42.000Z","msg":"中共既logic<br />\n永遠都係控制 &gt; 教育<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f987428c9ec0d5e0cd828df59b5df23b2ae98b7e","tid":1695033,"uid":55458,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T11:55:10.000Z","msg":"你成年都扣你信用啦<br />\n垃圾國家一定要殲滅"},{"pid":"16bd79fb67c23291c74b0655f0ab41787ae1fc3a","tid":1695033,"uid":32577,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T12:08:15.000Z","msg":"點解唔禁哂所有人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 全球外掛數量應該會大減"},{"pid":"a95bcb88a402624074a946da41cf70a789d79024","tid":1695033,"uid":289565,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T12:37:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁細個都識偷人錢 係咪中国教育出現問題"},{"pid":"4aee3f6f71ce1fe7a1449ca19529cf2d6ba7363d","tid":1695033,"uid":293097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cdf139c33d2ee6253e14b497402d4ec7a7f8c1a4","tid":1695033,"uid":263261,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T11:53:42.000Z","msg":"中共既logic<br />\n永遠都係控制 &gt; 教育<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T19:59:27.000Z","msg":"因為教育會教到佢地分對錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有思考  反了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中共：還是禁制好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}